teff_gspphot.description: Effective temperature from GSP-Phot Aeneas best library using BP/RP spectra

mh_gspphot.description: Iron abundance from GSP-Phot Aeneas best library using BP/RP spectra

distance_gspphot.description: Distance from GSP-Phot Aeneas best library using BP/RP spectra

mg_gspphot.description: Absolute magnitude $M_{\rm G}$ from GSP-Phot Aeneas best library using BP/RP spectra

radius_gspphot.description: Radius from GSP-Phot Aeneas best library using BP/RP spectra

teff_gspspec.description: Effective temperature from GSP-Spec MatisseGauguin using RVS spectra and Monte Carlo realisations

teff_espucd.description: Effective temperature estimate from ESP-UCD based on the RP spectrum

radius_flame.description: Radius of the star from FLAME using {\tt teffGspphot} and {\tt lumFlame}

lum_flame.description: Luminosity of the star from FLAME using G band magnitude, extinction ({\tt agGspphot}),  parallax or distance, and a bolometric correction {\tt bcFlame}

mass_flame.description: Mass of the star from FLAME using stellar models, {\tt lumFlame}, and {\tt teffGspphot}

age_flame.description: Age of the star from FLAME using stellar models, see {\tt massFlame} for details

distance_msc.description: Distance from MSC using BP/RP spectra and parallax

teff_msc1.description: Effective temperature of the primary from MSC using BP/RP spectra and parallax

teff_msc2.description: Effective temperature of the secondary from MSC using BP/RP spectra and parallax
